<https://www.gov.uk/government/people/esme-winch> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "Esme Winch joined the Further Education (FE) Commissioner team in 2019 as an FE Adviser. She was appointed Deputy FE Commissioner in January 2026. She has held a number of roles in the FE sector including: Group Finance and Resources Director, NCG Managing Director and Chief Financial Officer, NCFE Chief Executive and Principal, Loughborough College"@en .
